# Mapping

This directory contains the notebook used to generate spatial predictions of soil organic carbon (SOC) stocks across Florida’s grazing lands and to analyze the drivers of SOC variability using explainable machine learning.

---

## Files

### Mapping.ipynb

This notebook performs spatial prediction and model interpretation based on the trained SOC model.

The notebook includes two main components:

---

1. SOC Spatial Prediction

2. SHAP-Based Model Interpretation

---

## Notes

All scripts are implemented as **Jupyter notebooks** to facilitate reproducibility and transparency of the mapping workflow.
